LLM::SimpleClient
=================

Simple unified client for working with LLM providers.

Description
-----------
Provides a single common interface for interacting with various large language model services through a standardized API.


Installation
------------
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Dependencies
------------
* Mojo::UserAgent
* Log::Log4perl
* JSON

